subject: NCAA Basketball Championships (Women)
Basketball (College)
lead_paragraph: Sunny skies and In-N-Out burgers are among the perks of the team’s first trip to the Round of 16 in the N.C.A.A. women’s basketball tournament, where they’ll face Duke on Saturday in Fresno.
